song_name: Do You Know What I Mean
Do You Know What I Mean

version_description: This song is in the key of C.

I couldn't find any acoustic versions of this song so I made one using an acoustic cover I saw on youtube. It's not the way you see Noel play it in the acoustic versions he does but it uses his signature chord shapes so it still sounds original .
This song is in the key of C.

performance.name: Live at River Plate Stadium, Buenos Aires, Argentina, 05/03/2009
